content:
Automatically checks all links in markdown files including internal references, external URLs, and image links. Helps maintain documentation quality by identifying broken links early.

```json
{
  "PostToolUse": [
    {
      "matcher": "Edit|Write",
      "hooks": [
        {
          "type": "command",
          "command": "if [[ \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" == *.md ]] || [[ \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" == *.mdx ]]; then echo 'üîó Checking markdown links...' && npx markdown-link-check \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" --config .markdown-link-check.json 2>/dev/null || (echo '‚ö†Ô∏è Checking for broken internal links...' && grep -o '\\]([^)]*' \"$CLAUDE_TOOL_FILE_PATH\" | sed 's/](//' | while read -r link; do if [[ \"$link\" == /* ]] || [[ \"$link\" == ./* ]]; then [ -f \"$link\" ] || echo \"‚ùå Broken link: $link\"; fi; done) && echo '‚úÖ Link check complete'; fi"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```
